==English==

===Adjective===

'''phlegmatic'''

#Watery.
#Abounding in phlegm; as, phlegmatic humors; a phlegmatic constitution.
#Generating or causing phlegm.
#Not easily excited to action or passion; cold; dull; sluggish; heavy; as, a phlegmatic person.

